# Part 2: Planning

Plan command reference, phase planning workflow, `.planning/` storage, visualization — see [`references/planning-workflow.md`](references/planning-workflow.md).

Canonical planning API:

```bash
task-board q --format compact 'plan(EPIC-01, mode=children)'   # project/epic/story planning model
task-board q --format compact 'plan(TASK-01, mode=related)'     # task/bug + dependency closure
```

Local CLI facade:

```bash
task-board plan                                    # full project plan
task-board plan EPIC-01                            # epic plan
task-board plan EPIC-01 --render --format png      # render hierarchy graph
task-board plan EPIC-01 --render --layout phases   # render phases graph
task-board plan --render --active                  # active elements only
