description:Fix ReluxAnalytics AppMetrica aggregator activation handling. The aggregator stores the boolean result of AppMetrica activation, but identify and track currently continue to set identity/report events even if activation returned false. This can send calls through an inactive or misconfigured AppMetrica client and hides activation failure semantics from tests.
